    <h4>R: <u>57</u> G: <u>211</u> B: <u>199</u></h4>
  </div>

  <div class="step2">
    <h4>R: 57 = 10<sup>1</sup> x 5 + 10<sup>0</sup> x 7</h4>
    <h4>G: 211 = 10<sup>2</sup> x 2 + 10<sup>1</sup> x 1 + 10<sup>0</sup> x 1</h4>
    <h4>Now try converting the BLUE (B) value: </h4>
  
    <p>B: 199 = 10<sup><input type="input" id="exp1" maxlength="1" size="1" value=""></sup> x <input type="input" id="co1" maxlength="1" size="1" value=""> + 10<sup><input type="input" id="exp2" maxlength="1" size="1" value=""></sup> x <input type="input" id="co2" maxlength="1" size="1" value=""> + 10<sup><input type="input" id="exp3" maxlength="1" size="1" value=""></sup> x <input type="input" id="co3" maxlength="1" size="1" value=""></p>
  
    <button onclick="validate(199, 10, [exp1, co1, exp2, co2, exp3, co3])">Submit</button>

    <input type='text' id="custom"/>
  </div>

